5-individuals-short-entry: In Tibetan astrology, a unique method has been developed for describing the state of a person in terms of 5 individual forces.
About-astrological-indicators:
In the Norbu horoscope, astrological readings are divided into: 
Health
Business
Circumstances
Lunar Days
Haircuts
Travel
 
The Health, Business and Travel sections are based on personal data and depend on your date of birth. 

The Circumstances, Haircuts and Lunar Days sections are general and the same for everyone.

Sometimes there are disagreements about personal and general indicators, which is normal for Tibetan Astrology. In this case, personal indicators of "Health" and "Business" take first priority. "Circumstances" and " Lunar Day" have less influence.
About-lunar-days: Lunar days are calculated according to the Pug-Pa system, and correspond to the calculations of the Institute of Tibetan Medicine and Astrology Men-tsi-Khang (Dharmzala, India). In this system the lunar day corresponds to solar days and shifts with a dawn, therefore sometimes there are double lunar days and sometimes the lunar day is missing.
About-text:
All calculations for the horoscope are based on important, proven sources. Tibetan Calendar is good to use as a useful recommendation source, but to make important decisions please consider your own circumstances.
Norbu means "Jewel" in Tibetan.

common_horo_aquarius: Aquarius, this phase prompts personal growth. Embrace change and focus on your unique ideas. Collaborate for success. Career shines, but stay balanced. Relationships flourish with honesty. Health: prioritize self-care. Trust your intuition. Exciting times ahead!
common_horo_aries: The new month brings you a lot of energy and inspiration. You are ready to embark on new adventures and showcase your initiative. Be cautious and remember to maintain balance â€“ despite your enthusiasm, don't forget to exercise caution when making decisions. In your work, be persistent, but respect your colleagues' opinions. In your personal life, it's a time for romance, so enjoy those moments together.
common_horo_cancer: Embrace change this cycle. New opportunities await, but adaptability is key. Trust your intuition for financial decisions. Nurture existing relationships, and be open to meeting new, influential connections. Your emotional intelligence will guide you to success.
common_horo_capricorn: Capricorn, be ready for a transformative period. Trust your intuition, as new opportunities may arise. Balance work and personal life to maintain harmony. Embrace change with optimism, it could lead to long-term success. Stay open to advice from trusted allies for a prosperous future.
common_horo_gemini: This period encourages Gemini to embrace change and explore new opportunities. Your communication skills are on point, making it a great time for networking and connecting with others. Trust your intuition in decision-making. A creative project could bring success and recognition. Stay adaptable and open-minded.
common_horo_leo: Leo, a fiery lion, your charisma knows no bounds. The stars forecast a time of self-discovery. Embrace your creative side, and your passions will flourish. Financially, be cautious; don't be too generous. Health is good; focus on fitness. Love could bring surprises - be open to new connections.
common_horo_libra: Balancing act ahead. Career prospects shine; seize opportunities. Relationships thrive, but don't neglect self-care. Embrace change with grace. Financial gains likely. Trust your instincts. Focus on your goals; success is within reach.
common_horo_pisces: Pisces, this period encourages self-reflection and spiritual growth. Trust your intuition and pay attention to dreams. Relationships may need extra care; be open to communication. Your creative energy is high, use it to pursue your passions. Focus on self-care for balance and well-being.
common_horo_sagittarius: This period, Sagittarius, you're full of energy and inspiration. Your adventurous spirit shines. Embrace new opportunities, travel, and expand your horizons. Your charisma draws people closer, fostering meaningful connections. Stay open to change, as it brings growth and success.
common_horo_scorpio: Your intensity and determination will shine this cycle. Embrace change and let go of the past. Personal growth is favored. Trust your instincts; they'll lead you to success. Financial opportunities may arise, so be prepared to seize them. Love is in the air; deepen connections.
common_horo_taurus:
Dear Taurus, your determination will lead to success. Embrace change and trust your instincts. Your financial prospects look promising, but avoid impulsive spending. In love, communication is key. Stay grounded and focus on self-care for balance. Lucky numbers: 5, 15, 22.

Remember that astrology is for entertainment and reflection purposes, and it's not a science. Make your decisions based on sound judgment and critical thinking.
common_horo_virgo: Virgo, your meticulous nature will shine this period. Your attention to detail will bring success in work and relationships. Embrace change with optimism, and remember to take time for self-care. Health is a priority, so maintain a balanced lifestyle. Opportunities await, seize them!

la-description:
"La" - the protective energy - is responsible for the integrity and harmony of the personality. 

Very weakened La corresponds to a state of burnout and depression. 

The La energy is mobile and circulates through the body. 
La provides interconnection with external energies of the outside world.
La_position_card_description:
It is better to avoid surgeries on the areas of the body where the LA is located.

LA is a protective energy responsible for the integrity and harmony of the personality.

The LA energy is moving and circulates through the body.

LA energy location is indicated according to the three systems of the Tibetan calendar: Zurkar, Darmo and Mipam.

lung-description:
Lungta (Lung Ta) - fortune
Fortune is usually associated with good external circumstances. When the relationship of our internal and external energies is harmonious, no unfavorable circumstances can invade our life. Symbolizes happiness, good luck, and the ability to avoid unfavorable situations.
